data.title: Where would you live if you had to choose between Östersund, Sundsvall, Umeå and Luleå?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 5): Depends on what you are looking for.

Östersund - some great skiing close by. Dry inland weather. They have the lake. Cold and dark.

Sundsvall - paper mill town. They have the sea. Cold and dark.

Umeå - university town. They have the river. Colder and darker.
